      "content": "but honestly i really just want to know if the drops will help in the meantime. it's not like i'm losing vision or anything, just a bit of discomfort. can i just use them 4 or 5 times a day to keep the eye moist until i can get a break from work? it shouldn't hurt to try them, right?",
